snippet.title: Hyper Gods Announcement Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Frantic dogfights! Awesome combos! 2D CHAOS!! A God is reborn and keen on fulfilling the prophecy of the Armageddon. Become the only mercenary to hold off the End of Days.

Check it out on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/423730
